title: Alex Morse Speaks Out, Plus Kamala Harris as Biden's VP
description:
Massachusetts congressional candidate Alex Morse joins the show to discuss his perspective on the misconduct allegations against him. Katie and Matt discuss Biden's selection of Kamala Harris as his running mate.
